Subject: Secunia Research: Cyrus IMAPd NTTP Authentication Bypass Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 05/10/2011

      - Cyrus IMAPd NTTP Authentication Bypass Vulnerability -

======================================================================
Table of Contents

